<p>Perfect!</p>
<p>Let's add our properties, <code>private $id;</code>, <code>private $title;</code> for the movie title, 
<code>private $samsCharacterName</code> for Sam's character, <code>private $rating</code> to give the
movie appearance a rating, <code>private $isMainCharacter</code> so we can see if Sam was the
lead in that movie, and lastly <code>private $releasedAt</code> which will tell us exactly when
the movie came out.</p>
