<h2 id="generate-orm-annotations">Generate ORM Annotations <a class="headerlink" href="doctrine#generate-orm-annotations" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Now that we have these we can go back to command n, search ORM and select
"Generate ORM annotations". Select all of the fields that are in the menu and hit
ok:</p>
