<p>Awesome! Each field has all its annotations! Even better than that, it recognizes
that <code>id</code> is our primary key so it set that up and it noticed that <code>$isMainCharacter</code>
is probably a boolean, because of the 'is' in the beginning. And it also saw that
<code>$releasedAt</code> is a <code>datetime</code>. This isn't perfect, I would prefer <code>$releasedAt</code> to
just be a date, and rating up here is not a string, but an integer:</p>
