<p>Even though I had to move that manually, what's really cool is that it's highlighting and
saying "Yo! Your repository Class is messed up! You can't use the short class name because
now it's in a different namespace." I can delete what's there  and type <code>MovieRepository</code>
and I get autocomplete on the entire name:</p>
